title: Call or Text Beautiful two-story home w/pool, full upstairs wood deck
posting_body: ['Beautiful two-story home w/pool, full upstairs wood deck balcony, with a lovely lake view.', 'Spacious 4 bedroom, 2 Bath, one half bath, updated home, with updated kitchen, baths, floors.', 'Home has large Master Suite w/ sitting area/ French doors, his/her walk-in closets & renovated master bath.', 'Spacious covered terrace, 3 car garage, accordion shutters on all windows and doors in a gated community.', 'Home has been well maintained by original owners.', 'CABEL AND INTERNET included.', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'Helping people find rentals since 2012!', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'We specialize in Broward County Rentals.', 'I can text you a list of all the rentals available in the area.', 'Fast approval, NO HOA for some properties.', 'Pet friendly for some!', 'Proof of income is the most  important thing.', 'We can help people with bad credit or no credit!', "Let me know what you're looking for and I will find the right place regardless of the situation!", 'Brittini Flinn', 'SUN OCEAN REALTY', 'NO EMAIL', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'PLEASE REFER TO TYN112449101']
